<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 06:08:59 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>新西兰将禁止一次性电子烟，以防止未成年人养成这种习惯</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/new-zealand-to-ban-disposable-e-cigarettes-in-a-bid-to-prevent-minors-from-taking-up-the-habit/articleshow/108636517.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108636517.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;新西兰禁止销售一次性电子烟，提高未成年人罚款，支持电子烟戒烟。人们对青少年吸电子烟表示担忧。零售商面临罚款、图像和名称禁令等销售限制。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 05:24:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/new-zealand-to-ban-disposable-e-cigarettes-in-a-bid-to-prevent-minors-from-taking-up-the-habit/articleshow/108636517.cms</guid></item><item><title>联合国：以色列可能利用饥饿作为“战争武器”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-may-be-using-starvation-as-weapon-of-war-un/articleshow/108635849.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108635849.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;联合国周二表示，以色列严格限制向饱受战争蹂躏的加沙提供援助，再加上其军事进攻，可能相当于利用饥饿作为“战争武器”，这将构成“战争罪”。她指出，战前加沙基本上“不存在”营养不良问题。联合国人权事务高级专员沃尔克·特克谴责加沙地区猖獗的饥饿和迫在眉睫的饥荒。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 05:00:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-may-be-using-starvation-as-weapon-of-war-un/articleshow/108635849.cms</guid></item><item><title>3 月 20 日法语日：主题、意义以及如何庆祝</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/french-language-day-on-march-20-theme-significance-and-how-to-celebrate/articleshow/108634768.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108634768.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; 3 月 20 日的法语日在全球范围内推广法语和文化，具有丰富的历史影响和国际意义，通过庆祝活动和保护工作将世界各地的法语人士联系起来。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 04:57:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/french-language-day-on-march-20-theme-significance-and-how-to-celebrate/articleshow/108634768.cms</guid></item><item><title>2024 年全球最幸福国家</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/worlds-happiest-countries-full-list-and-where-india-stands/articleshow/108633024.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108633024.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;芬兰继续保持最幸福国家的地位，丹麦和冰岛也名列前茅。阿富汗仍垫底，而美国跌出前 20 名。哥斯达黎加和科威特有所改善。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 03:06:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/worlds-happiest-countries-full-list-and-where-india-stands/articleshow/108633024.cms</guid></item><item><title>特朗普支持全国禁止怀孕15周左右堕胎</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-supports-national-ban-on-abortions-around-15-weeks-of-pregnancy/articleshow/108632741.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108632741.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国前总统唐纳德·特朗普公开支持在全国范围内禁止怀孕 15 周内堕胎，这是他首次明确支持特定的时间限制。特朗普批评民主党不支持此类限制，并暗示可能在 15 周内达成共识。关于州与联邦对堕胎政策的监管的争论愈演愈烈。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 03:00:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-supports-national-ban-on-abortions-around-15-weeks-of-pregnancy/articleshow/108632741.cms</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜声称在开发旨在攻击关岛的高超音速导弹方面取得进展</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/north-korea-claims-progress-in-development-of-hypersonic-missile-designed-to-strike-guam/articleshow/108632347.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108632347.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据官方媒体周三报道，朝鲜成功测试了新型中程高超音速导弹的固体燃料发动机，并声称在开发一种更强大、更敏捷的导弹方面取得了进展，该导弹旨在打击该地区遥远的美国目标。高超音速导弹是朝鲜领导人金正恩公开誓言要在 2021 年推出的一系列高科技武器系统之一，以应对他所说的美国日益加深的敌意。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 02:37:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/north-korea-claims-progress-in-development-of-hypersonic-missile-designed-to-strike-guam/articleshow/108632347.cms</guid></item><item><title>两名巴基斯坦矿工遇难，八人恐因瓦斯爆炸而死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/two-pakistan-miners-killed-8-feared-dead-in-gas-explosion/articleshow/108632226.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108632226.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴基斯坦南部一座因瓦斯爆炸导致 10 名工人被困的倒塌矿井中，救援人员打捞出两具尸体。在不安全的条件下，我们继续努力寻找失踪人员。原因是一氧化碳气体积聚。悲惨事故凸显了巴基斯坦矿山安全措施的缺乏。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 02:27:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/two-pakistan-miners-killed-8-feared-dead-in-gas-explosion/articleshow/108632226.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦发生5.5级地震</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/earthquake-5-5-magnitude-shakes-pakistan/articleshow/108631815.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108631815.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 01:56:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/earthquake-5-5-magnitude-shakes-pakistan/articleshow/108631815.cms</guid></item><item><title>布林肯在南海争端中对马尼拉的支持“铁定”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/support-to-manila-iron-clad-blinken-amid-scs-row/articleshow/108631034.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108631034.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;布林肯在马尼拉会见官员时重申了美国在南海冲突后的支持。拜登计划与马科斯和日本首相举行峰会，以解决对中国在印太地区行动的担忧。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 23:59:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/support-to-manila-iron-clad-blinken-amid-scs-row/articleshow/108631034.cms</guid></item><item><title>比比回绝拜登，并发誓要继续袭击拉法</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/bibi-rebuffs-biden-vows-to-go-ahead-with-rafah-assault/articleshow/108630993.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108630993.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 23:57:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/bibi-rebuffs-biden-vows-to-go-ahead-with-rafah-assault/articleshow/108630993.cms</guid></item><item><title>针对纽约市长的性侵犯案</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/sexual-assault-case-filed-against-new-york-mayor/articleshow/108630640.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108630640.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 23:45:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/sexual-assault-case-filed-against-new-york-mayor/articleshow/108630640.cms</guid></item><item><title>旁遮普邦的“事实上的CM”？纳瓦兹主持玛丽亚姆政府会议</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/punjabs-de-facto-cm-nawaz-chairs-maryams-govt-meetings/articleshow/108630518.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108630518.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 23:42:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/punjabs-de-facto-cm-nawaz-chairs-maryams-govt-meetings/articleshow/108630518.cms</guid></item><item><title>博尔索纳罗被指控伪造新冠疫苗数据，这是他的第一份起诉书</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/bolsonaro-charged-with-falsification-of-covid-vax-data-his-1st-indictment/articleshow/108630388.cms</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 23:37:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/bolsonaro-charged-with-falsification-of-covid-vax-data-his-1st-indictment/articleshow/108630388.cms</guid></item><item><title>特朗普前助手因颠覆民意调查开始入狱</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-ex-aide-begins-jail-time-for-poll-subversion/articleshow/108630199.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108630199.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;彼得·纳瓦罗因参与颠覆 2020 年选举而在迈阿密监狱服刑。批评拜登政府，提出有关行政特权的法律问题，但法官们仍然不为所动。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 23:31:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-ex-aide-begins-jail-time-for-poll-subversion/articleshow/108630199.cms</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯三号人物、该组织“国防部长”在以色列袭击中丧生</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hamas-no-3-groups-defence-minister-killed-in-israel-strike/articleshow/108629979.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108629979.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 23:24:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hamas-no-3-groups-defence-minister-killed-in-israel-strike/articleshow/108629979.cms</guid></item><item><title>那是凯特吗？新的模糊视频未能阻止王室谣言</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/is-that-kate-new-blurry-video-fails-to-halt-royal-rumour-mill/articleshow/108629812.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108629812.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;凯特王妃与威廉王子在温莎农场商店的术后首段视频成为全球头条新闻。尽管这次郊游取得了成功，但社交媒体仍然对其真实性持怀疑态度。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 23:18:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/is-that-kate-new-blurry-video-fails-to-halt-royal-rumour-mill/articleshow/108629812.cms</guid></item><item><title>胡塞武装称红海油轮遭到导弹袭击</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/houthis-say-fuel-tanker-in-the-red-sea-targeted-with-missiles/articleshow/108626393.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108626393.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 18:11:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/houthis-say-fuel-tanker-in-the-red-sea-targeted-with-missiles/articleshow/108626393.cms</guid></item><item><title>破冰：科学家们如何尝试从一百万英里外为欧几里得的视野除冰</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/home/science/breaking-the-ice-how-scientists-are-trying-to-de-ice-euclids-vision-from-a-million-miles-away/articleshow/108623701.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108623701.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 14:28:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/home/science/breaking-the-ice-how-scientists-are-trying-to-de-ice-euclids-vision-from-a-million-miles-away/articleshow/108623701.cms</guid></item><item><title>斯里兰卡在选举年推进选举改革</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/sri-lanka-moves-for-electoral-reforms-in-election-year/articleshow/108622162.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108622162.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;科伦坡批准议会选举制度改革，建立混合代表制。此举是在即将举行的总统选举之前进行的，并有可能提前举行议会选举。政治消息人士称，可能会举行新的议会选举。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 13:02:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/sri-lanka-moves-for-electoral-reforms-in-election-year/articleshow/108622162.cms</guid></item><item><title>白金汉宫否认俄罗斯有关查理国王去世的报道</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/buckingham-palace-denies-russian-report-of-king-charles-demise/articleshow/108620032.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108620032.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;有关国王查理三世去世的报道在俄罗斯媒体平台上广泛传播，英国驻乌克兰大使馆和白金汉宫迅速予以否认。据《卫报》报道，这一虚假谣言在与俄罗斯著名报纸《Vedomosti》相关的 Telegram 频道上分享后引起了关注。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 12:25:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/buckingham-palace-denies-russian-report-of-king-charles-demise/articleshow/108620032.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>